---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import site from "../../data/site.json";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description={`The story behind ${site.businessName}.`}>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container prose">
      <h1>Our Story</h1>
      <p>
        {site.businessName} started the way most good baking stories do: a home kitchen, a
        favorite family recipe, and more pie than one household could possibly eat. Friends and
        neighbors kept asking for "just one more," and eventually that turned into a small
        cottage food business.
      </p>
      <p>
        Every pie, cookie, and loaf is made in small batches with real ingredients, no shortcuts,
        and the same care you'd expect from a friend's kitchen rather than a factory line. We bake
        to order as much as possible, so what you get is fresh, not sitting on a shelf.
      </p>
      <p>
        {site.businessName} operates as a licensed home-based cottage food operation. That means
        smaller batches, a shorter menu, and a lot more attention paid to each item that goes out
        the door.
      </p>
      <p>
        Have a question, a special request, or want to place an order? Reach out any time at{" "}
        <a href={`mailto:${site.contactEmail}`}>{site.contactEmail}</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 70ch;
  }
</style>
